query:
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.slug, p.createdAt, c.name as category_name
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN categories c ON p.categoryId = c.id
WHERE c.slug = 'blessed-protective-artifacts'
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10;
